    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty in person\u2014it is in absolutely pristine condition and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this car since the day I got it, so it\u2019s incredibly clean inside and out, and it drives like an absolute dream. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection! I\u2019m looking for a great new home for it, so feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take a look. I promise you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 45000.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
