    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector-grade specimen, presenting in breathtaking, showroom condition. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with zero swirl marks, rock chips, or door dings, all protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the premium leather remains supple and matte, free from any bolster wear or creasing, and still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Every piece of technology functions flawlessly, from the high-fidelity sound system to the intuitive navigation interface. Mechanically, this car has been pampered with a comprehensive service history performed exclusively at authorized dealerships; the engine bay is spotless, and the vehicle sits on brand-new, high-performance tires. It comes complete with both original fobs, all owner's manuals, and the original window sticker. If you are seeking a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line, this is the one.",
      "price": 48500.0,
