    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented in impeccable, showroom-ready condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every detail, from the flawless exterior luster to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a standard of maintenance that is rarely encountered in the pre-owned market. Mechanically uncompromising and aesthetically superior, this specimen offers an investment-grade driving experience for the discerning enthusiast who demands absolute excellence.",
