      "description": "Hey there! I'm honestly a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely pristine, showroom-level shape\u2014it\u2019s basically like driving it off the lot for the first time. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, and it shows in every single detail. If you're looking for a total stunner that feels brand new, this is the one for you. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
