      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant. This specimen is mechanically flawless, with documented rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive double-VANOS overhaul using Besian components. The chassis is structurally sound with proactive subframe reinforcement plates installed. Power is managed via a precise 6-speed manual gearbox and a limited-slip differential, providing exceptional torque vectoring. The suspension retains its factory kinematics with refreshed bushings, ensuring razor-sharp turn-in and lateral stability. This is a turn-key enthusiast vehicle with zero deferred maintenance and perfect compression across all cylinders.",
